    </div>
</section>

<section class="xs-col-12 lg-col-9 pt1 mb4 pt2">
  <h2 class="mb1 bold">Body</h2>
  <label class="block type-4">Body text, or <code class="js-highlight">p</code>, is the base font size for our typographic system. You can also use the class <code class="js-highlight">.type-4</code> to style any element as body text. Optimal line length for body text should be no longer than (x) characters.</label>

